      org.springframework.http.ResponseEntity<Object> getSampleProcessing(String fromDate, String toDate, String currentUIDate, com.agaramtech.qualis.global.UserInfo userInfo, int nprojecttypecode) throws Exception
      This DAO interface declaration will access the DAO layer that is used to retrieve list of all active storagesampleprocessing for the logged in site.
      Parameters:
      fromDate - [String] From Date.
      toDate - [String]To Date.
      currentUIDate - [String] Current Date.
      userInfo - [UserInfo] ntranssitecode [int] primary key of site object for which the list is to be fetched
      nprojecttypecode - [int] Project Type Code.
      Returns:
      response entity object holding response status and list of all active storagesampleprocessing for the logged in site.
      Throws:
      Exception - that are thrown from this DAO layer

      Returns:
